<main>
    <div class="container" id="main-content">

        <h1>Complete the Permanent Impairment Lifestyle Questionnaire</h1>
        
        <p>Your permanent impairment compensation is calculated by looking at how your impairment affects your life. To do this, we use a lifestyle rating and your permanent impairment medical reports.</p>

        <p>Your medical reports are used to create your permanent impairment points.</p>
        <p>To calculate your lifestyle rating we'd like you to complete this self-assessment Lifestyle Questionnaire.</p> 
        <p>In the questionnaire you will assess how your impairment affects 5 aspects of your life. You will give yourself an overall rating at the end of each section.</p>
        There sections are:
        <ul>
            <li>personal relationships</li>
            <li>mobility</li>
            <li>recreation</li>
            <li>employment</li>
            <li>domestic</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Each section should take around 10 to 15 minutes to complete, depending on your circumstances.</p>
        
        
        <div class="tip--wrapper">
            <p>You can save your answers at any time and come back to complete your questionnaire later. </p>
        </div>


        <h2>Your permanent impairment conditions</h2>
        This questionnaire relates to your accepted conditions:
        <ul>
            <li>Hearing loss </li>
            <li>Tinnitus</li>
            <li>Lumbar Spondylosis</li>
            <li>Mild anxiety</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Get DVA to assess you</h2>
        <p>Instead of completing the questionnaire, you can get the Department of Veterans' Affairs (DVA) to give you a lifestyle rating. However, the Lifestyle Questionnaire will let you provide more detail on how your life has been affected by your impairment.</p>



        <hr />

        <fieldset>
            <legend class="legend-label">You can choose to complete the Lifestyle Questionnaire or get a DVA lifestyle rating.</legend>
            <div class="radio-toggle">
                <label class="on label-left" for="do-questionnaire-yes" style="width: 260px;"><input id="do-questionnaire-yes" type="radio" name="do-questionnaire"><span>Complete lifestyle questionnaire</span></label>
                <label class="off label-right" for="do-questionnaire-no" style="width: 260px;"><input id="do-questionnaire-no" type="radio" name="do-questionnaire"><span>Get a DVA lifestyle assessment</span></label>
            </div>
        </fieldset>

        <div class="pagination">
            <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '#open-modal'">Cancel claim</button>
            <div class="floated">
                <button class="uikit-btn btnNext" id="btnNext" onclick="window.location.href = '/pi-claim1'" disabled>Save and next</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
